prodNameC: 邦迪斯迷你那夫人類免疫球蛋白 G4 套組
ingredientsDesc:
MININEPH HUMAN IgG4 REAGENT
Consisting of monospecific antiserum coated onto polystyrene microparticles. Supplied in lyophilised form, it contains 0.099% sodium azide as a preservative.
MININEPH IgG4 SWIPE CARD
This is encoded with details of the reaction curve specific to the respective lot of reagent. This card is reagent lot specific and must be used only with this lot of reagent.

MININEPH IgG4 BUFFER
For use with this lot of IgG4 reagent only. Contains 0.099% Sodium azide as a preservative.
MININEPH HUMAN IgG4 HIGH AND LOW CONTROLS
These consist of pooled normal human serum and are supplied in stabilised liquid form. They contain 0.099% sodium azide, 0.1% EACA and 0.01% benzamidine as preservatives.
applicantName: 太暘生物科技股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 新北市汐止區福德三路369號12樓
efficacy: 試劑組提供體外檢測人體血清當中的免疫球蛋白質IgG亞型：IgG4，可協助臨床診斷人體內IgG4不正常的代謝情況，套組適用於MININEPH TM 濁度計做為實驗操作平台。
